### Learn AngularJS In A Week!

That is the goal. I plan to learn AngularJS by 
* reading the book "AngularJS Up & Running" by Shyam Seshadri & Brad Green
* Watching YouTube Videos
* Record progress on this wiki website.

I have never used GitHub before, and this will be part of objectives.

I plan to record my journey here in this directory as well.
